snippet.title: The Groundz - Gameplay footage
snippet.description: Set in a Oakland, CA circa 1993, The Groundz is a street dodge ball game where players smash on each other at Parks and Rec's and Youth Development Centers all across the city. Smash on opponents in a 2 vs. 2 with friends but, either way we'll see you on The Groundz.
